{"tid":2019089,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"畜龍衫唔屬於警察制服，咁即係人人都可以買返嚟著？？？","createTime":"2020-05-16T04:52:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T05:25:14.000Z","uid":121100,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"820daa67dc258211114d96dc9df6e25464f30665","tid":2019089,"uid":121100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T04:52:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7kO6PFk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7kO6PFk.jpg&h=69aad6a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n眾新聞 CitizenNews<br />\n<br />\n眾聞<br />\n<br />\n監警會報告：速龍裝束非警隊制服　不受《警察通例》 規管<br />\n<br />\n撰文: 眾新聞記者 | 發佈日期: 15.05.20<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n自去年6月反送中運動爆發以來，警暴問題引起關注。然而，無論軍裝、便衣警員，還是俗稱「速龍小隊」的特別戰術小隊，在執勤時往往不表明身份，未有在制服上展示警員編號或配戴委任證，令人質疑警方藉此逃避問責。<br />\n監警會今日（15日）就《逃犯條例》修訂草案引發的大型公眾活動及相關的警方行動，發表專題審視報告，指「速龍小隊」戰術裝束並不界定為警隊制服， 不受《警察通例》或《警察程序手冊》規管，警方從未指示「速龍小隊」成員將展示警員編號的布肩章繫於戰術裝束。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/29915/%E9%80%9F%E9%BE%8D%E5%B0%8F%E9%9A%8A-%E7%9B%A3%E8%AD%A6%E6%9C%83-%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D-29915/%E7%9B%A3%E8%AD%A6%E6%9C%83%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%EF%BC%9A%E9%80%9F%E9%BE%8D%E8%A3%9D%E6%9D%9F%E9%9D%9E%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D-%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%97%E3%80%8A%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E9%80%9A%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%8B-%E8%A6%8F%E7%AE%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F29915%2F%25E9%2580%259F%25E9%25BE%258D%25E5%25B0%258F%25E9%259A%258A-%25E7%259B%25A3%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259C%2583-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%259A%258A%25E5%2588%25B6%25E6%259C%258D-29915%2F%25E7%259B%25A3%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A%25EF%25BC%259A%25E9%2580%259F%25E9%25BE%258D%25E8%25A3%259D%25E6%259D%259F%25E9%259D%259E%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%259A%258A%25E5%2588%25B6%25E6%259C%258D-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%2597%25E3%2580%258A%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E9%2580%259A%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%258B-%25E8%25A6%258F%25E7%25AE%25A1&d=I